text: Vitaliy Martsiv (born 19 June 1983) is a Ukrainian cross-country skier. He competed in the men's sprint event at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian male cross- country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Ukraine Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:People from Sumy
